Project 1 test run record / capture checklist

The assignment asks for one typescript file showing correct inputs and graceful
error handling. On a Linux machine, create the real transcript by running:

cd Prj1
script -a test-runs/typescript

Then run the commands below. When finished, type:

exit

Commands to record:

make clean
make

printf "11111111111111110000000000000000\n101010\n" > data/small.txt
./bin/MyCompress data/small.txt data/small.comp
./bin/MyDecompress data/small.comp data/small.out
./bin/ForkCompress data/small.txt data/fork.comp
./bin/PipeCompress data/small.txt data/pipe.comp
./bin/ParFork data/small.txt data/parfork.comp 4
./bin/ParThread data/small.txt data/parthread.comp 4

printf "ls\nexit\n" | ./bin/MiniShell
printf "ls -l data\nexit\n" | ./bin/MoreShell
printf "ls -l | wc\nexit\n" | ./bin/DupShell

sh questions-1-10/10-timing-comparison/run_times.sh

Graceful error commands to record:

./bin/MyCompress missing.txt data/out.txt
./bin/MyDecompress missing.txt data/out.txt
./bin/ForkCompress missing.txt data/out.txt
./bin/PipeCompress missing.txt data/out.txt
./bin/ParFork missing.txt data/out.txt 4
./bin/ParThread missing.txt data/out.txt 4
printf "not_a_real_command\nexit\n" | ./bin/MiniShell
printf "not_a_real_command arg\nexit\n" | ./bin/MoreShell
printf "not_a_real_command | wc\nexit\n" | ./bin/DupShell
